Frontend Features

Modern React App with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS
All Required Pages: Home, About, Portfolio, Blog, Services, Careers, Clients, Contact
Responsive Design that works perfectly on all devices
Beautiful Animations using Framer Motion
Professional UI matching your logo colors (Blue primary, Red secondary)
Interactive Components with hover effects and smooth transitions

Backend Features

Complete Node.js API with Express.js
MongoDB Database with proper schemas for all data
Email Integration with Nodemailer for all contact forms
Admin Panel with JWT authentication for content management
Security Features including rate limiting, validation, and CORS
All API Endpoints for blogs, contacts, careers, testimonials, and clients

Key Functionality

Contact Forms that send emails to your specified addresses
Career Applications with resume upload capability
Blog System with categories, search, and featured posts
Portfolio Showcase with filtering and project details
Client Management with testimonials and ratings
Service Pages for Deliver, Bring, Express, and Package services



